title: Quick Chermoula & Cheese Topped Chicken with Tomato & Radish Couscous
description: Get ready for some flavour combinations because there are some all-time favourites in this meal. Chermoula
seasoned chicken is always very tasty but let's try roasting it with cheese for a winning blend of flavours. Serve with a tomato and radish couscous for a perfectly paired dinner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

